      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it's a total dream! This car is in truly spectacular shape; it honestly looks and feels like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and well-maintained, and I'm looking for a new owner who will appreciate how pristine it is. It runs perfectly and is ready to hit the road today. You\u2019ve really gotta see this one in person to believe it!",
