    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a masterclass in lightweight engineering, featuring the iconic 13B-REW twin-rotor engine with its sequential Hitachi turbocharger setup intact and functioning flawlessly. The power delivery is linear, transitioning seamlessly as the secondary turbine engages. The chassis remains true to its 50/50 weight distribution, supported by an original, unmolested double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line is tight, and the apex seals maintain factory-spec compression. This specimen boasts original paint and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear or UV damage, representing a rare opportunity to own a mechanically pristine legend of the Golden Era.",
      "price": 46500.0,
