      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, presenting in breathtaking, showroom condition. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the original 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Included with the sale are all original keys, factory manuals, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance records. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic that has been pampered since day one.",
